{"lemma":"دِرَّةُ","slug":"دِرَّةُ","root":"د.ر.ر","root_slug":"د-ر-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/د-ر-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n12325","n12326","n12327",""],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AF%D9%90%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pearl","tags":["singulative"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"parakeet, a variety of parrot","tags":["singulative"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"teat, udder"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"milk"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Related to the verb دَرَّ (darra, “to flow copiously, to accrue”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n12325","headword_ar":"دَرَّةٌ","root":"dr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dir~apN","text_ar":"دِرَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n12326","headword_ar":"دُرَّةٌ","root":"dr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dur~N","text_ar":"دُرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n12327","headword_ar":"دِرَّةٌ","root":"dr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dar~N","text_ar":"دَرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", first sentence. ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Copious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abundant, flowing milk; milk flowing copiously,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abundantly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a flow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stream,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a flowing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"streaming, of milk;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its abundance"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abounding:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K:) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dar~apN","text_ar":"دَرَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (L:) or this latter signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a single flow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stream, of milk."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) Hence the prov.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA A=tiyka maAA@xotalafati Ald~ir~apu waAljir~apu","text_ar":"لَا ا=تِيكَ مَاا@خْتَلَفَتِ الدِّرَّةُ وَالجِرَّةُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will not come to thee as long as the flow of milk and the cud go"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the former]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"downwards and"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the latter]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upwards."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jir~apu","text_ar":"جِرَّةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b3-  [Hence also the phrase,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lils~aHaAbi dir~apN","text_ar":"لِلسَّحَابِ دِرَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The clouds"},{"kind":"page_break","n":864},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"have a pouring forth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dirarN","text_ar":"دِرَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) En-Nemir Ibn-Towlab says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"waraHomatuhu wasamaA='N diraro \n                      \n                     \n                        salaAmu AlA_ilaAhi warayoHaAnuhu"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAtu dirarK","text_ar":"ذَاتُ دِرَرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The peace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"security,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of God, and his bounty, and his mercy, and a sky pouring forth showers"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) Some say that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dirarN","text_ar":"دِرَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAr~N","text_ar":"دَارٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flowing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"streaming;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flowing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"streaming, copiously,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abundantly"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiyamFA","text_ar":"قِيَمًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the Kur vi. 162 signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAy^imFA","text_ar":"قَايِمًا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) In like manner one says also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diyamN dirarN","text_ar":"دِيَمٌ دِرَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Lasting and still rains pouring down"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lils~uwqi dir~apN","text_ar":"لِلسُّوقِ دِرَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The market has a brisk traffic going on in it, its goods selling much."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lils~aAqi dir~apN","text_ar":"لِلسَّاقِ دِرَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The thigh,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shank,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of the horse or the like]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"has a continuous movement for running;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lilojaroYi","text_ar":"لِلْجَرْىِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisotidoraArN","text_ar":"اِسْتِدْرَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (AZ, S.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mar~a Alfarasu EalaY dir~atihi","text_ar":"مَرَّ الفَرَسُ عَلَى دِرَّتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The horse passed along without being turned aside by anything."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musotadir~N","text_ar":"مُسْتَدِرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dir~apN","text_ar":"دِرَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Blood"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as being likened to milk]. (K.) A poet cited by Th likens war and the blood thereof to a [raging] she-camel and her"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dir~ap","text_ar":"دِرَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b7-  And (assumed tropical:) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"means of subsistence"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as being likened to milk]. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gr","text_ar":"غر"},{"kind":"text","text":". [See an ex. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gir~apN","text_ar":"غِرَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b8-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner, of flowing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"streaming, of milk."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain thing with which one beats,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flogs;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kr, S, A, K, TA;) i. e. the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dir~ap","text_ar":"دِرَّة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the Sultán:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a whip:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) [app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a whip for flogging criminals;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as seems to be implied in the TA: I have not found any Arab who can describe it in the present day: it seems to have been"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a kind of whip,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scourge, of twisted cords"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thongs, used for punishment and in sport, such as is now called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"firoqil~ap","text_ar":"فِرْقِلَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":": or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a whip made of a strip,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"broad strip,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see 1 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xfq","text_ar":"خفق"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of thick and tough hide,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"it is described by Golius and Freytag (by the latter as from the S and K, in neither of which is any such explanation found,) as “"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strophium ex fune aliave re contortum,"},{"kind":"text","text":"aut"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nervus taurinus, similisve res, quibus percuti solet:"},{"kind":"text","text":"”] an Arabic word, well known: (TA:) [or an arabicized word, from the Pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dur~aho","text_ar":"دُرَّهْ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dirarN","text_ar":"دِرَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A, Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","S","Msb","K","L"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}